I've tracked the problem down to PHPUnit_Util_PHP::getPhpBinary(). Instead of returning the correct php bin path, it returns the daemon and watchr bin paths. These are the the paths specified in $_SERVER['_'], which is the file that launched the phpunit. I've fixed this on my installation through a hack as I can't find a way to reliably retrieve the correct php binary.

``` php
